ISLAMABAD, Nov 24 (APP):The government has finalised Anti Rape Investigations and Trial Bill for expeditious punishment of rapists through special courts, said Advisor to the Prime Minister on Accountability and Interior Barrister Mirza Shahzad Akbar in a tweet.
He said the main aim of the bill is to protect the rape victims besides maintaining record of the rapists.The constitution of special courts, proposed in the bill, would help prompt trial and effective prosecution of the rape cases.
